title: Ian Miller from Kowloon Walled City and Less Art
itunes:title: Ian Miller from Kowloon Walled City and Less Art
description:
Episode 249 - My dude, Ian Miller is on the show this week. He plays in bands like Kowloon Walled City, Less Art, Redemption 87, Skankin Pickle and many more. He has incredible stories and a wild journey to where he is at now. A true definition of a lifer and I am stoked to have him on the show. Use our Amazon Affiliate Code to support the show!
